            "id": "4575068",
            "title": "Snapshot of Quant and Wall St. ratings for quantum computing stocks after Nvidia's latest push",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Quantum computing stocks rallied on Tuesday after <span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Nvidia</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span></span></span></span>) unveiled a new suite of open-source AI models to tackle key bottlenecks in quantum systems, reigniting investor enthusiasm for the emerging sector.</p>\n<p><span>The </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20472509-nvidia-launches-ising-the-world-s-first-open-ai-models-to-accelerate-the-path-to-useful\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"NVIDIA Ising\">NVIDIA Ising</a> is <span>designed to help researchers and enterprises build quantum processors capable of running useful applications. It targets two of quantum computing’s greatest challenges—error correction and system calibration—potentially making quantum machines more practical and scalable.</span></p>\n<p>The rally was broad-based across pure-play names, with IonQ (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IONQ\" title=\"IonQ, Inc.\">IONQ</a></span></span></span></span>) jumping roughly 16%, Rigetti Computing (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RGTI\" title=\"Rigetti Computing, Inc.\">RGTI</a></span></span></span></span>) gaining over 10%, and D-Wave Quantum (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QBTS\" title=\"D-Wave Quantum Inc.\">QBTS</a></span></span></span></span>) rising about 13%, reflecting heightened optimism that AI could accelerate the commercialization timeline for quantum technologies.</p>\n<p><span>Taking a snapshot of </span><span>Quant ratings and Wall Street ratings on pure-play quantum computing stocks and also companies that are not pure-play but heavily invested in quantum. </span></p>\n<p><span>Pure-play quantum computing stocks:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">IonQ</span> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IONQ\" title=\"IonQ, Inc.\">IONQ</a>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IONQ/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2.62\">2.62</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IONQ/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.46\">4.46</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Quantum Computing</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QUBT\" title=\"Quantum Computing Inc.\">QUBT</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QUBT/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"1.44\">1.44</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QUBT/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.20\">4.20</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Rigetti Computing</span> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RGTI\" title=\"Rigetti Computing, Inc.\">RGTI</a>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RGTI/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"1.44\">1.44</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RGTI/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.25\">4.25</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">D-Wave Quantum</span> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QBTS\" title=\"D-Wave Quantum Inc.\">QBTS</a>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QBTS/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"1.28\">1.28</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QBTS/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.78\">4.78</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">SEALSQ Corp</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LAES\" title=\"SEALSQ Corp\">LAES</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LAES/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"1.13\">1.13</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LAES/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.50\">4.50</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Arqit Quantum</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARQQ\" title=\"Arqit Quantum Inc.\">ARQQ</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARQQ/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"1.05\">1.05</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARQQ/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"5.00\">5.00</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Infleqtion</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INFQ\" title=\"Infleqtion, Inc.\">INFQ</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - NA; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INFQ/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"5.00\">5.00</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span>Big tech with quantum exposure:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Nvidia</span> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA/ratings/quant-ratings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.48\">3.48</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.71\">4.71</a><span class=\"whitespace-normal\"></span>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"990\" data-section-id=\"1bzozp4\" data-start=\"942\">\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Microsoft</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSFT\" title=\"Microsoft Corporation\">MSFT</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSFT/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.48\">3.48</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MSFT/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.71\">4.71</a>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1049\" data-section-id=\"pvjaae\" data-start=\"991\">\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Alphabet</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOG)</a> - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOG/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.48\">3.48</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOG/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"4.61\">4.61</a></span>\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Intel</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.46\">3.46</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.16\">3.16</a><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"></span>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1099\" data-section-id=\"1lv6o9e\" data-start=\"1050\">\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">International Business Machines</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBM\" title=\"International Business Machines Corporation\">IBM</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBM/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.10\">3.10</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBM/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.86\">3.86</a>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1251\" data-section-id=\"1h3n4wt\" data-start=\"1202\">\n<span class=\"whitespace-normal\">Honeywell International</span> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HON\" title=\"Honeywell International Inc.\">HON</a></span></span></span>) - Quant rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HON/ratings/quant-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\".09\">3.09</a>; Wall Street rating - <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HON/ratings/sell-side-ratings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3.96\">3.96</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
